IT’S MORNING.

00:06:22.105 --> 00:06:27.048
Deusolbert: IT IS THE ONE MEMORY
I HAVE LEFT OF MY PAST.

00:06:27.115 --> 00:06:30.955
I CANNOT EVEN RECALL
WHEN IT WAS OR WHO.

00:06:31.022 --> 00:06:33.927
THOUGH YOU ARE LONG GONE,

00:06:33.994 --> 00:06:36.934
I WILL PROTECT
THE WORLD WE SHARED.

00:06:37.001 --> 00:06:40.307
THIS, I SWEAR.

00:06:40.374 --> 00:06:43.413
ENHANCE ARMAMENT!

00:06:46.786 --> 00:06:48.457
♪♪

00:07:02.218 --> 00:07:05.624
I AM DEUSOLBERT
SYNTHESIS SEVEN!

00:07:05.691 --> 00:07:10.167
WHOSOEVER STANDS BEFORE ME
SHALL BE BURNED TO ASHES!

00:07:20.621 --> 00:07:21.857
( goblins yell )

00:07:21.923 --> 00:07:23.593
( screaming )

00:07:36.653 --> 00:07:37.488
( Deusolbert grunts )

00:07:41.763 --> 00:07:43.433
( goblins scream )

00:08:00.001 --> 00:08:01.703
Bercouli: FIRST, WE’LL RESTORE

00:08:01.769 --> 00:08:03.673
THE ORDER
OF THE INTEGRITY KNIGHTS.

00:08:03.740 --> 00:08:06.913
THEN WE’LL MUSTER THE IMPERIAL
KNIGHTS OF THE FOUR EMPIRES

00:08:06.980 --> 00:08:08.551
AND TRAIN THEM FOR BATTLE.

00:08:08.617 --> 00:08:09.886
THERE’S STRENGTH IN NUMBERS,

00:08:09.953 --> 00:08:12.425
AND RIGHT NOW,
WE NEED ALL THE HELP WE CAN GET.

00:08:12.492 --> 00:08:15.998
I KNOW WHAT I TOLD YOU
IS HARD TO ACCEPT,

00:08:16.065 --> 00:08:18.637
BUT IT’S STILL OUR JOB
TO PROTECT THE PEOPLE HERE.

00:08:18.703 --> 00:08:20.574
I CAN’T DO THAT WITHOUT YOU.

00:08:22.045 --> 00:08:23.747
Fanatio: COMMANDER...

00:08:23.814 --> 00:08:25.617
I SHALL FOLLOW YOU
WHEREVER YOU GO.

00:08:32.966 --> 00:08:33.934
FOUND HIM.

00:08:34.002 --> 00:08:36.072
ENHANCE ARMAMENT!

00:08:37.141 --> 00:08:39.712
PIERCE HIM! DIVINE LIGHT!

00:08:41.382 --> 00:08:42.585
Sigurosig: EH?

00:08:42.652 --> 00:08:44.589
( chorus vocalizing )

00:08:51.936 --> 00:08:54.742
( giant groans )

00:08:54.809 --> 00:08:57.548
( Sigurosig gasping )

00:09:01.423 --> 00:09:03.961
Fizel: OOH!
THE FIGHTING’S STARTED!

00:09:04.028 --> 00:09:05.130
Linel: YUP, YUP!

00:09:05.197 --> 00:09:07.001
