Linel: THE VICE COMMANDER’S
KILLED BUNCHES, TOO.

00:09:11.643 --> 00:09:13.180
- Fizel: WHAT’S WITH THEM?
- Linel: YEAH,

00:09:13.247 --> 00:09:15.551
THE LEFT FLANK SEEMS
A BIT WEAK, DOESN’T IT?

00:09:15.618 --> 00:09:19.792
Fizel: MM-HMM. SURE,
ELDRIE HAS AMAZING SKILLS,

00:09:19.859 --> 00:09:22.965
BUT AS A KNIGHT, HE’S NEVER BEEN
IN A BATTLE LIKE THIS BEFORE.

00:09:23.033 --> 00:09:25.838
Linel: AND THEN THERE’S
RENLICCHI BEHIND HIM,

00:09:25.905 --> 00:09:27.541
NOT THE MOST RELIABLE.

00:09:27.608 --> 00:09:29.546
Fizel: POOR THING.
HE’D BE BETTER OFF

00:09:29.612 --> 00:09:31.717
ALL THE WAY IN BACK
WITH THE SUPPLY CORPS.

00:09:31.784 --> 00:09:33.087
Linel: SPEAKING OF,

00:09:33.153 --> 00:09:35.223
I HEARD THAT KIRITO BOY’S
SITTING BACK THERE.

00:09:37.729 --> 00:09:38.463
( both giggle )

00:09:42.104 --> 00:09:43.673
- ( goblins growling )
- Kosogi: STAY TOGETHER!

00:09:43.740 --> 00:09:46.279
FOLLOW MY LEAD,
AND DON’T STOP FOR ANYTHING!

00:09:46.346 --> 00:09:48.283
♪♪

00:09:50.354 --> 00:09:53.059
Eldrie: DO NOT
LET A SINGLE ONE PAST US!

00:09:53.126 --> 00:09:54.562
CUT THEM ALL DOWN!

00:09:54.629 --> 00:09:55.498
Soldiers: YES, SIR!

00:09:55.565 --> 00:09:57.568
( Kosogi growling )

