Soldier: HUH?

00:10:11.095 --> 00:10:13.633
- ( soldiers yelp )
- Eldrie: WHAT IN BLAZES...

00:10:16.039 --> 00:10:17.975
Kosogi: GET DOWN! KEEP RUNNING!

00:10:18.043 --> 00:10:20.947
( goblins growling )

00:10:21.015 --> 00:10:22.752
Soldier 2: GET BACK HERE,
YOU FILTHY--

00:10:22.819 --> 00:10:25.457
Eldrie: NO! YOU’LL STRIKE DOWN
ONE OF OURS IN ALL THIS SMOKE!

00:10:27.294 --> 00:10:29.832
THEY’RE HEADED
FOR THE REAR UNIT.

00:10:29.899 --> 00:10:32.571
I PRAY SIR RENLY
CAN HOLD THEM AT BAY.

00:10:38.750 --> 00:10:41.022
Soldier 2: THE LEFT FLANK
HAS BEEN BREACHED BY GOBLINS!

00:10:41.089 --> 00:10:42.591
THEY ARE ON THEIR WAY!

00:10:43.861 --> 00:10:44.896
WHERE IS SIR RENLY?

00:10:44.963 --> 00:10:45.898
( soldiers mutter )

00:10:45.965 --> 00:10:47.135
Soldier 3: WE DON’T KNOW.

00:10:47.201 --> 00:10:50.273
HE WAS HERE WHEN ALL
THE FIGHTING STARTED.

00:10:52.111 --> 00:10:53.847
( Renly panting )

00:10:57.457 --> 00:10:59.394
♪♪

