( Deusolbert grunts )

00:11:03.469 --> 00:11:05.206
( goblins screaming )

00:11:08.446 --> 00:11:11.586
Shibori: THAT ONE!
THAT ARCHER THERE!

00:11:11.653 --> 00:11:13.591
SURROUND HIM,
AND STOMP HIS BONES!

00:11:13.658 --> 00:11:15.794
( goblins yelling )

00:11:27.484 --> 00:11:29.488
Golgorosso:
PROTECT SIR DEUSOLBERT!

00:11:29.556 --> 00:11:31.158
DON’T LET
ANY OF THE WRETCHES THROUGH!

00:11:31.225 --> 00:11:33.530
Deusolbert: THANK YOU.
I’LL HURRY.

00:11:33.597 --> 00:11:35.433
Golgorosso: WE WON’T FAIL YOU.

00:11:35.500 --> 00:11:37.437
( soldiers yelling )

00:11:47.658 --> 00:11:48.593
( Deusolbert grunts )

00:11:48.660 --> 00:11:50.396
( goblins screaming )

00:11:55.541 --> 00:11:58.045
( giants gasping )

00:12:16.516 --> 00:12:19.488
Sigurosig:
HOW COULD A HUMAN DO THIS?

00:12:19.556 --> 00:12:22.628
I’VE NEVER FELT
SUCH FEAR BEFORE.

00:12:22.695 --> 00:12:24.231
IT CAN’T BE.

00:12:24.298 --> 00:12:26.603
- ( static crackling )
- IT CAN’T BE.

