IT CAN’T BE. IT CAN’T BE.

00:12:28.239 --> 00:12:31.345
IT CAN’T BE. IT CAN’T BE.
IT CAN’T BE.

00:12:31.412 --> 00:12:33.551
KILL. KILL. KILL.

00:12:33.617 --> 00:12:36.355
KILL. KILL. KILL. KIL--

