KILL! KI-KI-KILL!

00:12:39.394 --> 00:12:41.064
KILL!

00:12:43.235 --> 00:12:44.438
( yells )

00:12:44.506 --> 00:12:45.641
( giants groaning )

00:12:45.708 --> 00:12:49.181
