Sigurosig: KILL! KILL! KILL!

00:13:02.508 --> 00:13:03.577
Fanatio: WHY?

00:13:03.643 --> 00:13:06.148
Sigurosig: KILL THE HUMAN! KILL!

00:13:06.215 --> 00:13:07.551
KILL! KILL!

00:13:07.618 --> 00:13:08.987
( Fanatio grunts )

00:13:12.628 --> 00:13:13.763
Sigurosig: KI-L!

00:13:16.402 --> 00:13:17.136
Fanatio: COMMANDER.

