KILL!

00:15:07.290 --> 00:15:10.162
♪♪

00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:24.057
( gasping )

00:15:25.594 --> 00:15:29.267
KILL THE HUMAN!

00:15:29.334 --> 00:15:31.639
Fanatio: YOUR GRAVE AWAITS YOU.

00:15:44.632 --> 00:15:47.270
( giants gasping )

00:16:04.706 --> 00:16:07.578
FIRST UNIT, CENTER, ADVANCE!

00:16:07.645 --> 00:16:09.481
PUSH THE ENEMY BACK!

