00:16:30.561 --> 00:16:33.534
I CANNOT EVEN TELL
HOW LONG WE’VE BEEN FIGHTING.

00:16:39.078 --> 00:16:42.384
( goblins scream )

00:16:42.451 --> 00:16:45.257
( Deusolbert panting )
