00:16:45.324 --> 00:16:47.428
THEY KEEP RUSHING
TO THEIR DEATHS.

00:16:47.495 --> 00:16:48.965
HMM?

00:16:49.031 --> 00:16:51.269
( sighs )

00:16:51.336 --> 00:16:53.139
Shibori: LOOK WHAT WE GOT HERE,

00:16:53.206 --> 00:16:56.445
AN ARCHER WITH NO MORE ARROWS.

00:16:58.349 --> 00:17:00.420
♪♪

00:17:07.267 --> 00:17:10.273
Deusolbert: YOU ARE A CHIEF
