00:17:10.340 --> 00:17:11.677
ONE OF THE COUNCIL OF TEN?

00:17:11.744 --> 00:17:13.279
Shibori: THAT’S RIGHT,

00:17:13.346 --> 00:17:16.519
CHIEF OF THE FLATLAND GOBLINS,
LORD SHIBORI!

00:17:19.592 --> 00:17:22.632
Deusolbert:
I AM AN INTEGRITY KNIGHT,

00:17:22.699 --> 00:17:24.268
DEUSOLBERT SYNTHESIS SEVEN--

00:17:24.334 --> 00:17:28.777
Shibori: SO WHAT?! I DON’T CARE
WHAT YOUR NAME IS, IUM!

00:17:28.844 --> 00:17:30.582
YOU’RE JUST MEAT TO ME,

00:17:30.648 --> 00:17:34.154
AND ONCE I CHOP OFF YOUR HEAD,
YOU’LL MAKE A FINE MEAL!

00:17:34.221 --> 00:17:36.627
ENOUGH TALK!
RUSH HIM, AND HOLD HIM!

00:17:36.694 --> 00:17:38.598
( goblins yelling )

00:17:38.664 --> 00:17:41.169
Deusolbert: HOW ABSURD!

00:17:41.235 --> 00:17:43.339
- ( grunts )
- ( goblin groans )

00:17:46.412 --> 00:17:47.347
( goblin yells )

00:17:47.414 --> 00:17:48.282
( gags )

00:17:51.189 --> 00:17:53.225
Deusolbert: THAT LEAVES FOUR.

00:18:03.748 --> 00:18:05.517
( goblins chuckle )

