- Soldier: COMMANDER.
- Bercouli: HMM?

00:19:42.645 --> 00:19:45.083
Soldier: LADY FANATIO
KILLED THE GIANT’S CHIEF.

00:19:45.150 --> 00:19:47.923
SIR DEUSOLBERT
KILLED A GOBLIN CHIEF.

00:19:47.989 --> 00:19:49.324
THEY’RE HOLDING THE LINE NOW.

00:19:49.391 --> 00:19:52.097
Bercouli: MM. WHAT ELSE?

00:19:52.164 --> 00:19:55.738
Soldier: WELL, MY LORD,
AS YOU CAN SEE,

00:19:55.805 --> 00:19:58.342
THE ENEMY FORCES OUTNUMBER US.
WE’RE HOLDING THEM OFF,

00:19:58.409 --> 00:20:01.282
